metadata.name: H.E.R.O.I.C. NFTs #1
metadata.description: HA! Studios are excited to announce that we’re launching into the NFT space with the debut of our FIRST collection totaling 11,000 H.E.R.O.I.C. NFT’s! We want to reward our community with a token of our appreciation by releasing Letter “H” to our early supporter who are here to help us grow. We are in this together as Heroicites and will own 240 of this collection. There will be a gaming utility that will integrate with your NFT. Skies the limit
